"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":781,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/14\/sahabah-tabieen-salaf-salih\/","url_meta":{"origin":6041,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salaf: Best generations are the companions, successors","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas'ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"The best people are those of my generation, then those who come after them, then those who come after them. Then, there will come people after them whose testimony precedes their oaths and their oaths precede their\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31885,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/ahmad-speaking-badly-sahabah\/","url_meta":{"origin":6041,"position":3},"title":"Ahmad on Sahaba: Speaking badly of the Companions is against Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdul Malik ibn Maymun reported: Ahmad ibn Hanbal, may Allah have mercy on him, said to me, \u201cIf you see a man speaking badly about any of the companions of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, be wary of his practice of Islam.\u201d Source: Ta\u0304ri\u0304kh Dimashq\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":285,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/12\/24\/patience-prophet-companions-famine\/","url_meta":{"origin":6041,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Famine: Patience of the Prophet, companions with famine","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 24, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"'Utbah ibn Ghazwan reported: I found myself as the seventh among seven who had been with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him. We had nothing to eat but the leaves of a wild tree until the corners of our mouths were wounded. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2967\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19386,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/21\/brothers-of-prophet-all-believers\/","url_meta":{"origin":6041,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Companions: The Prophet is the brother of all believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 21, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI wish I could meet my brothers.\u201d The companions of the Prophet said, \u201cAre we not your brothers?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYou are my companions, but my brothers are those who have faith in me\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self"